OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy with showery outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain through the evening and
OL,8,Fovernight. Some drier, clearer spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping for a time for Orkney
OL,10,Fovernight. Strong southeast winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy to start with some
OL,13,Fpatchy rain. Otherwise bright spells
OL,14,Fand scattered showers, these heavy and
OL,15,Fperhaps thundery at times. Breezy.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA dry
OL,18,Fstart Friday with rain pushing east
OL,19,Flater. Bright spells and showers on
OL,20,FSaturday. Mostly dry, bright Sunday,
OL,21,Fchance of the odd shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
